data.title: Awesome place to be
data.text: Bartenders are always happy to see people and always friendly.  I love the patio.  It's nice to sit outside with friends and have since drinks.  There did is pretty good too!

owner_response.author: Johnnierich, Owner at Emmett's, responded to this review
owner_response.text: Thanks for the review. We try to keep our place friendly and enjoyable for all of our customers.
owner_response.title: Owner Response
